---
import PricingTable from './PricingTable.astro';
---

<div class="space-y-12">
  <section>
    <h3 class="t-label" style="color: var(--color-ink-3);">
      Itemised pricing with a centrally-published fee (canonical)
    </h3>
    <p
      class="t-body mt-2"
      style="color: var(--color-ink-2); font-size: 14px; max-width: 70ch;"
    >
      The NSW Owner Builder pricing — a fixed course fee, an included
      certificate, and a permit fee linked out to the regulator page.
    </p>
    <div
      class="mt-3 px-6 py-6"
      style="border: 1px solid var(--color-rule); background: var(--color-bg);"
    >
      <PricingTable
        heading="How much does the course cost?"
        rows={[
          { item: 'ABE Education course fee', cost: '$180' },
          { item: 'AlertForce Statement of Attainment', cost: 'Included' },
          {
            item: 'Building Commission NSW permit fee',
            cost: 'Set by Service NSW',
            costHref: 'https://www.nsw.gov.au/business-and-economy/licences-and-credentials',
          },
          { item: 'White Card (if you do not hold one)', cost: 'Separate course' },
        ]}
        caption="Course fee verified with ABE Education on 28 April 2026. Permit fees are set by the regulator."
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h3 class="t-label" style="color: var(--color-ink-3);">
      Sale pricing with RRP and a total row
    </h3>
    <p
      class="t-body mt-2"
      style="color: var(--color-ink-2); font-size: 14px; max-width: 70ch;"
    >
      A struck-through RRP on the first row and an emphasised
      <code>total</code> row showing the all-inclusive price.
    </p>
    <div
      class="mt-3 px-6 py-6"
      style="border: 1px solid var(--color-rule); background: var(--color-bg);"
    >
      <PricingTable
        heading="White Card course cost"
        rows={[
          { item: 'White Card course (CPCWHS1001) via Zoom', cost: '$101', rrp: '$149' },
          { item: 'SafeWork NSW card processing fee', cost: '$28 (included)' },
        ]}
        total={{ item: 'You pay', cost: '$129' }}
        caption="Course fees are set by the training provider and subject to change. Confirm pricing at the time of booking."
      />
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
